{"tid":2375382,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Asus ROG Phone 5 試玩片，機背有個小屏幕","createTime":"2021-01-22T03:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T18:42:34.000Z","uid":114547,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3bd4600e80b393b51776ede17ffc338a1ff93896","tid":2375382,"uid":114547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:57:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bdjw0WTcrLs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fbdjw0WTcrLs&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TWg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=009c7870\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bdjw0WTcrLs</a><br />\n<br />\n2021 年才過去不到 1個月，各大廠商搭載 Snapdragon 888 的旗艦機不是正在發售就是在準備發售的路上，當然，這顆旗艦處理器Phone 可不能錯過，ASUS 與騰訊聯合製作的 ROG Phone 系列也有了消息。<br />\n<br />\n今早，網上曝光了一段據稱為 ROG Phone 5 的真機拍攝的影片，由片中可見新一代的 ROG Phone 5 在外觀設計上延續了前作的設計風格，後殼疑似採用玻璃物料，因其背部中央有一個數字5，推測其可能會跳過華人比較忌諱的數字「4」，直接將新機命名為 ROG Phone 5。而另一位數碼博主放出了該機的真機試片，從片中可以看出，ROG Phone 5 將採用對稱式全面屏，前置鏡頭在屏幕上方黑邊的右上角，遊戲中不擋畫面。值得注意的是，影片非常明顯地點明該機背部擁有一個小屏幕，可以顯示不同的圖案，雖然沒有什麼用處還費電，但卻充滿了滿滿的 ROG 味道(就是浪費嘛)，電競科技風也更加的突出。<br />\n<br />\n規格方面，官方並沒有透露什麼，但根據此前的爆料信息匯總，ROG Phone 5 無疑會搭載Snapdragon 888 旗艦處理器，配備支援 60W/65W 極速快充的 6000mAh 超大電池。後置三鏡前置單鏡。屏幕則會採用 6.6吋左右的非曲面對稱式 OLED 全面屏，高更新率與採樣率跑不了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2021/01/20/asus-rog-phone-5-hands-on-video-showing-secondary-display/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2021%2F01%2F20%2Fasus-rog-phone-5-hands-on-video-showing-secondary-display%2F&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TWg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=861dbbb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2021/01/20/asus-rog-phone-5-hands-on-video-showing-secondary-display/</a>"},{"pid":"3cd5d8c85fd002437d5cb050e88441a9676d50fa","tid":2375382,"uid":72746,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:15:48.000Z","msg":"哦～ 中國品牌ASUS<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201219/ZWIDODVXMFE45CY3GMUPMF6WHQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201219%2FZWIDODVXMFE45CY3GMUPMF6WHQ%2F&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TWg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=9a568e5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201219%2FZWIDODVXMFE45CY3GMUPMF6WHQ%2F&h=9a0d7ed6\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201219/ZWIDODVXMFE45CY3GMUPMF6WHQ/</a>"},{"pid":"f76ee5cb4bc4a42756b53c374e7fb669c4ea39d8","tid":2375382,"uid":71913,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:31:15.000Z","msg":"888 chip 垃圾"},{"pid":"8adf7ca2b9f7ea9f2ce78bf904e2a8ca88e91103","tid":2375382,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:33:30.000Z","msg":"請立即停止購買ASUS產品，明確證據顯示ASUS已被中國控制<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2330340\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2330340</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b989f8121d65d8d20ebc58daf12a83e9569c0a87","tid":2375382,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:06:40.000Z","msg":"我只想買一款全屏，冇M字額冇挖孔屏手機"},{"pid":"efd7be30fbd9771ac48272035efe1f0df6a410e6","tid":2375382,"uid":17245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:06:20.000Z","msg":"skip左4 直接5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係終國人先咁多數未要避忌<br />\n<br />\nbtw 今次係未又起皮野 但用天馬屏"},{"pid":"a17f51ef6603648b0cfcaf5965fca00c5628a4dd","tid":2375382,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efd7be30fbd9771ac48272035efe1f0df6a410e6","tid":2375382,"uid":17245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:06:20.000Z","msg":"skip左4 直接5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係終國人先咁多數未要避忌<br />\n<br />\nbtw 今次係未又起皮野 但用天馬屏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:08:17.000Z","msg":"日本人同韓國人都會<br />\n<br />\n因為四字同死字同音"},{"pid":"9ed1530dd24d7067074a66744ead76e8380602f9","tid":2375382,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1